u Huệ Mẫn","Canti Lau Sek-Ming","Trương Triệu Huy","La Gia Lương","Wing Lam","Stella Wong","Wong Wai","Ng Gong","Ian Fang","Law Kwok-Wai","Lau Gwai-Fong","Kwan Ching","Lâm Gia Đống","Pak Yan","Chu Tit-Wo"],"director":["Lưu Gia Hào"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Châu Huệ Mẫn","name_vi":"Châu Huệ Mẫn","name_original":"Vivian Chow","tmdb_id":146624,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mejpx1shZduknSiB395pa4eR0mz.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/146624"},{"name":"Canti Lau Sek-Ming","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Canti Lau Sek-Ming","tmdb_id":1118407,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8W7DzkYAK75tdTevSvY15pd3RZe.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1118407"},{"name":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_vi":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_original":"Eddie Cheung Siu-Fai","tmdb_id":72732,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jTrBt3y43LsO8XYsQnWg8bdwsP2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/72732"},{"name":"La Gia Lương","name_vi":"La Gia Lương","name_original":"Gallen Lo Ka-Leung","tmdb_id":1223043,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6ZCTOMeRktYL7iTEz7lg7N3XXPc.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1223043"},{"name":"Wing Lam","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wing Lam","tmdb_id":556802,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kqNqz5PGJiLSv5s41N1YSkSCabR.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/556802"},{"name":"Stella Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Stella Wong","tmdb_id":2820880,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uakqdrCrld5sCMCOIpeCXIFjBjs.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2820880"},{"name":"Wong Wai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wong Wai","tmdb_id":943779,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mekHAh0mDXYRhg6Z9x4rt88YMzU.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/943779"},{"name":"Ng Gong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ng Gong","tmdb_id":1266032,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oSqLJxPGHqkFXWlwif8snbc5c8u.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themovied